<% @title = 'School Year' %>

<h3>School Year</h3>
<table border="0px">
  <tr>
    <td class="label">Name:</td>
    <td><%=h @school_year.name %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td class="label">Description:</td>
    <td><%=h @school_year.description %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td class="label">Start Date:</td>
    <td><%=h @school_year.start_date %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td class="label">End Date:</td>
    <td><%=h @school_year.end_date %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td class="label">Age Cutoff Month:</td>
    <td><%=h @school_year.age_cutoff_month %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td class="label">Registration Fee:</td>
    <td><%=number_to_currency @school_year.registration_fee %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td class="label">Early Registration Tuition:</td>
    <td><%=number_to_currency @school_year.early_registration_tuition %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td class="label">Tuition:</td>
    <td><%=number_to_currency @school_year.tuition %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td class="label">Tuition Discount for 3 or more child:</td>
    <td><%=number_to_currency @school_year.tuition_discount_for_three_or_more_child %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td class="label">Tuition Discount for PreK:</td>
    <td><%=number_to_currency @school_year.tuition_discount_for_pre_k %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td class="label">Tuition Discount for Instructor:</td>
    <td><%=number_to_currency @school_year.tuition_discount_for_instructor %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td class="label">Elective Class Fee:</td>
    <td><%=number_to_currency @school_year.elective_class_fee %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td class="label">Book / Material Charge:</td>
    <td>
      <%= link_to 'Edit Book Charge', {controller: '/admin/school_years', action: 'edit_book_charge', id: @school_year}, {class: 'button'} %>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td class="label">PVA Activities Fee:</td>
    <td><%=number_to_currency @school_year.pva_membership_due %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td class="label">CCCA Membership Due:</td>
    <td><%=number_to_currency @school_year.ccca_membership_due %></td>
  </tr>
</table>
<p>The following dates are related to registration fee proration.
<ul>
  <li>
    Early Registration Start Date - the date early registration starts.
    During early registration period, early registration tuition would be charged.
  </li>
  <li>
    Early Registration End Date - the date after which early registration is no longer available.
  </li>
  <li>
    Registration Start Date - the date regular registration starts.
  </li>
  <li>
    Registration 75 Percent Date - the date after which 75% of full tuition would be charged.
  </li>
  <li>
    Registration End Date - the date after which no registration is allowed.
  </li>
  <li>
    Refund 90 Percent Date - the date after which only 90% of full tuition would be refunded.
  </li>
  <li>
    Refund 50 Percent Date - the date after which only 50% of full tuition would be refunded.
  </li>
  <li>
    Refund End Date - the date after which no refund would be allowed.
  </li>
</ul>
</p>
<table border="0px">
  <tr>
    <td class="label">Early Registration Start Date:</td>
    <td><%=h @school_year.early_registration_start_date %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td class="label">Early Registration End Date:</td>
    <td><%=h @school_year.early_registration_end_date %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td class="label">Registration Start Date:</td>
    <td><%=h @school_year.registration_start_date %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td class="label">Registration 75 Percent Date:</td>
    <td><%=h @school_year.registration_75_percent_date %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td class="label">Registration End Date:</td>
    <td><%=h @school_year.registration_end_date %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td class="label">Refund 90 Percent Date:</td>
    <td><%=h @school_year.refund_90_percent_date %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td class="label">Refund 50 Percent Date:</td>
    <td><%=h @school_year.refund_50_percent_date %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td class="label">Refund End Date:</td>
    <td><%=h @school_year.refund_end_date %></td>
  </tr>
</table>

